  For each anchor (E=24,32,40, f=31):
  Scenario A: 20-step descent (no floor) → 20-step ascent
  Scenario B: floor descent → same-count ascent

  Scenario A  (near-boundary, no floor):
  Anchor | Steps | Bottom-E | Bottom-f | Recov-E | Recov-f | E-match | f-match
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      24 |    20 |        4 |       31 |      24 |      31 | YES     | YES
      32 |    20 |       12 |       31 |      32 |      31 | YES     | YES
      40 |    20 |       20 |       31 |      40 |      31 | YES     | YES

  Scenario B  (through-floor, absorbing):
  Anchor | Steps | Bottom-E | Bottom-f | Recov-E | Recov-f | E-off | f-match
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      24 |    26 |        0 |        0 |      26 |       0 |    +2 | NO (0 vs 31)
      32 |    34 |        0 |        0 |      34 |       0 |    +2 | NO (0 vs 31)
